criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  adult patients >=18 years of age;

          -  chronic renal anemia;

          -  not receiving renal replacement therapy.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  women who are pregnant, breastfeeding or using unreliable birth control methods;

          -  administration of any investigational drug within 30 days preceding the screening
             visit and during the run-in period.
